{
  "stem": "14897.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That they were willing to-- to let out some Jews who were relatives of some people in South America.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "A hotel called Hotel Polski was assigned for the meeting and negotiating place for this exchange.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And this hotel became off limits to the Gestapo, in the sense everybody was safe who came to that hotel.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And Jews who heard about-- of course, the families of these people from South America were no longer alive.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So these were papers which had just names on them, no pictures.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the German SS, the German Gestapo, and the Jewish Gestapo were selling places on these lists to-- to be members of these families, to whatever survivors showed up at the Hotel Polski.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't have enough money to get on those lists, as it turned out luckily, because nobody survive.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they also had a list which was cheaper because it seemed to be less official, so to speak, of people, Jews, who had relatives in-- in, at the time, Palestine, relatives who were willing to take them in.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, we legitimately did have such relatives in Palestine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we decided to try this because we did-- you know, you didn't know how long the war would last.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, it always seemed to me that it would never end.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It just seemed that way till the very end.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was really not a possib-- well, the two young men in the-- in that apartment, I remember flirting a little bit with one of them and he with me.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was the one who wanted to become a priest, by the way, so-- [LAUGHS] but nothing really serious.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I will tell you when-- when I tell you about the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
